description:
Sticky Notes app for Android that understands the linuxmint/sticky note file for
Sticky Notes + SyncThing = StyncyNotes

StyncyNotes is a simple Sticky Note application that supports some basic formatting features like those available in the linux mint "Sticky" application (see  https://github.com/linuxmint/sticky).

It stores notes and formatting in a simple local json file that takes the same format as the linuxmint Sticky, so if you happen to run this app on your desktop, you can use SyncThing to keep the two sets of notes in step.
